Each rectangle represents a match from 2016 to 2024, with the color intensity reflecting the attendance—lighter shades of purple signify larger crowds. White rectangles indicate matches where official attendance data is unavailable or where there was no attendance, such as the closed-door matches during the 2020 COVID-19 pandemic.
